  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">Which of the following expressions is equivalent to <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"the fraction with numerator x squared, minus 2 x, minus 5, and denominator x minus 3\"></span>&nbsp;</span>?</p>\n",
